short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A browser extension based anti-phishing system. Check out at https://somethingphishy.ddns.net/

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SomethingPhishy is a browser extension designed to enhance your browsing experience by providing real-time analysis and validation of website URLs. Developed as part of an undergraduate thesis project, this experimental extension aims to help users identify and avoid potentially malicious websites, phishing attempts, and malware threats.
